  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York City Building Footprints, 2026 is a polygon theme representing the perimeter extent of buildings in New York City as of March 2026. Columbia Libraries staff downloaded this dataset from the NYCMap Hub at https://nycmaps-nyc.hub.arcgis.com/datasets/nyc::building/about reprojected it to state plane coordinates and reformatted to the geopackage format in March of 2026. Additional information about the data may be found at https://github.com/CityOfNewYork/nyc-geo-metadata/blob/master/Metadata/Metadata_BuildingFootprints.md"
